Economic News' next headline!

546
00:33:08.260 --> 00:33:13.430
"Emperor Straw Hat Luffy Holds
Vegapunk Hostage on Egghead!

547
00:33:13.430 --> 00:33:15.600
Starts All-out War with the Marines!"

548
00:33:15.600 --> 00:33:17.850
If we frame a pirate as the perpetrator,

549
00:33:17.850 --> 00:33:22.310
