580
00:33:58.980 --> 00:34:01.640
Don't twist the truth and make up stories!

581
00:34:01.640 --> 00:34:03.650
Have you no sense of decency?!

582
00:34:04.770 --> 00:34:07.020
She's wearing my clothes!

583
00:34:07.020 --> 00:34:08.780
I'll never wash them again!

584
00:34:08.780 --> 00:34:10.650
What?! You're so lucky!

585
00:34:10.650 --> 00:34:12.990
– Princess Vivi!
– Princess Vivi!

586
00:34:13.910 --> 00:34:16.200
You were a real sob story till yesterday!

587
00:34:16.200 --> 00:34:20.000
Don't get all hoity-toity
and tell me how to do my job!

588
00:34:20.000 --> 00:34:22.460
The only one who can shake up the world...

589
00:34:23.370 --> 00:34:25.080
is me!

590
00:34:25.080 --> 00:34:27.300
It doesn't matter if it's true or not!

591
00:34:27.300 --> 00:34:31.800
The news is just entertainment!

592
00:34:38.340 --> 00:34:43.430
Running so long, lost track of just how long it’s been

593
00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:50.790
Collected scars while striving, not even trying, beneath my skin

594
00:34:51.290 --> 00:34:58.210
But in the back of my head the dream is not dead, I remember a map

595
00:34:58.290 --> 00:35:04.500
to a treasure still gleaming, it’s within our grasp

596
00:35:04.640 --> 00:35:11.410
Can you feel my heart? Feelings I impart

597
00:35:11.370 --> 00:35:18.520
The promises are there; they're deep down but still primed to share

598
00:35:18.650 --> 00:35:27.630
Peerless dreams kept close, the dreams that always matter most

599
00:35:27.810 --> 00:35:33.390
Before we set sail why not raise a toast?

600
00:35:33.500 --> 00:35:40.410
So I pen this note to you! Dear sunrise, I’ll see you soon

601
00:35:40.570 --> 00:35:47.600
See the smile I saw the day that I sang this song to you

602
00:35:47.580 --> 00:35:54.650
And regardless of our age, these mem’ries will still remain

603
00:35:54.550 --> 00:36:01.760
Won’t forget until this wish makes it to you
